{"tid":2014054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"癡線 比財務中介騷擾","createTime":"2020-05-12T17:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T03:09:48.000Z","uid":155887,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c764493d7cbb0181131ee16fdc4abf4ccbb1cc7","tid":2014054,"uid":155887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"是緣老母呢排停咗工 好等錢洗 ,但係衰在現金出糧 ,銀行借唔到<br />\n<br />\n老母上ig見到借錢中介就whatsapp 咗過去 , 仲影埋地址證明 身份證 同 屋企人嘅名同電話, 之後中介就話收咗錢之後要畀返40% 嘅費用, 冇打錯 係40%嘅貸款金額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我老母就係冇借到, 之後收到財務公司打嚟, 老母冇聽到, 我老母whatsapp 返中介話考慮下先, 之後中介不停whatsapp 同打電話嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話貸款批咗, 你就算冇要都當你收咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要畀40%, 我老母冇再理佢, 中介不停煩住老母<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益 請問我可以點幫我老母拆掂佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5909340b5c640b495f551e02db115dab16c7a17b","tid":2014054,"uid":109759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:53:41.000Z","msg":"幫佢還"},{"pid":"3a33727f43df8cc5dbae6327c0ca85594e6f71fa","tid":2014054,"uid":155887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"重點 冇簽過任何嘢 ,冇錄過任何音 ,冇應承過接受貸款 , 冇聽過財務公司電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893dd1e2ed020a2f815240b6de6b57fd6830f8e9","tid":2014054,"uid":93318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:56:08.000Z","msg":"唔洗理"},{"pid":"8b76b10732987dc2883b1484c86d7cb35ab37cb7","tid":2014054,"uid":85396,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:56:17.000Z","msg":"報警無用，告佢啦<br />\n借錢打官司屈佢賠翻筆俾你"},{"pid":"fa419f483c9b3055909121f1a8ca463f9b99600b","tid":2014054,"u